/-- Typography:

every web app, page Or an mobile application have its base font, color, bg-color
and so on...
we call it as typography of the project. We are following all suggestions from
the book "Refractoring UI - by Adam Wathan & Steve Schoger". Hereafter we call
it our 'bible'.


