/-- Padding: Referring page no. 82 - from-bible and tailwindcss.com

below padding values are standard padding values. Below padding values are 
example of small, medium, large and extra large devices. Based on below ratio we
continue using padding.

p means - padding-top, right, bottom and left - all sides
py means - padding top and padding bottom
px means - padding left and padding right

e.g.: padding: $py OR padding: $px OR padding: $p0

-- string p0: 6 8
-- string p1: 8 10
-- string p2: 12 16
-- string p3: 15 30
-- string py: 15 0
-- string px: 0 15



/-- Margin: Referring page no. 82 - from bible and tailwindcss.com

